  NNAAMMEE

    XIfEvent, XCheckIfEvent, XPeekIfEvent - check the event queue with a
    predicate procedure

  SSYYNNTTAAXX

    XIfEvent(display, event_return, predicate, arg)
          Display *display;
          XEvent *event_return;
          Bool (*predicate)();
          XPointer arg;

    Bool XCheckIfEvent(display, event_return, predicate, arg)
          Display *display;
          XEvent *event_return;
          Bool (*predicate)();
